\f2\cf10 39}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Selemias, Nat\u227?, Ada\u237?as, }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 40}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Macnadebai, Sasai, Sarai, }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 41}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Azarel, Selemias, Semarias, }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 42}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Salum, Amarias e Jos\u233?; }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 43}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?e dos filhos de Nebo: Jeiel, Matitias, Zabade, Zebina, Jadai, Joel e Benaia. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 44}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Todos esses tinham tomado esposas estrangeiras, e eles mandaram embora as esposas junto com os filhos.\par}}